{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5345b893b3","title":"周恩来陪同刚果（布）总理努马扎来参观北京国棉三厂的谈话纪要","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"73b4334d4c","index":0,"year":1967,"month":10,"day":3,"articleId":"5345b893b3","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"大联合","id":"18bf6a78fe","type":"主题"},{"name":"对外关系和政策","id":"2bffb53b5b","type":"主题"},{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"52d851d5d9","type":"title","text":"周恩来陪同刚果（布）总理努马扎来参观北京国棉三厂的谈话纪要","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c07a5678ad","type":"paragraph","text":"〖时间：十二点。根据回忆传达，有误记录负责。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"81e16f1314","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：厂内女同志多，为什么没有女代表，你看你们全是男的。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4c30b09f16","type":"paragraph","text":"三厂代表：（代表汇报三厂情况时说）我厂自建立以来年年月月完成任务。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1029768312","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：这样讲不对吧！这样讲不符合毛泽东思想，今年二、三季度不是没有完成计划吗？这是党内走资派和资产阶级反动路线把群众搞成两派对立造成的，除了以上原因外，再加上某些头头不是无产阶级的党性，而是资产阶级的派性。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b628d3741e","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：（汇报三厂文化大革命情况）群众全部投入了文化大革命。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e47a9ec4d1","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：全部投入了吗？一个也没有不参加的？没有逍遥派吗？打架可能有部分人没有参加。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7bc5b089ff","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：（汇报现在的情况）三厂坚决执行毛主席的“斗私批修”的最近最新指示。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b6e317903d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们解释什么是“私”字？结合厂内具体情况讲“私”字。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"461f5a50ad","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：……","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"62f1a02ece","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：还没有说出来！个人主义、小团体主义、风头主义……这些都是“私”字。（随后总理分别问是那一派的，有多少人，有多少代表。）","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4ba9ea4a60","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：革委会八个代表，东方红七个代表。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c3e23572f2","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：东方红这一点做得比较好，革委会比较小气，我就叫你们双方对等（各七个），自由战士也派一名，自由战士一定会支持革委会的。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f6bdb00f03","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们的生产计划订了没有？群众讨论了没有？你们应向纺织系统挑战，不但向北京挑战，而且还要向全国挑战。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c8082e51dd","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：现在出勤多少？","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"daa208382a","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：出勤率70%。","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"11679919fc","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：什么病最多？","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"30ce95ea34","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：高血压。","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b6de75f20c","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：高血压主要是打架打的，睡不着觉。休息几天就行了，不要相信医生。过去我们打了二十多年仗，经常睡不着觉，这也是无产阶级和资产阶级斗争。","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a13a69f48a","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：厂史上出勤最高多少？","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"294cb670e2","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：……","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a03ed816b0","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：最好95%，能不能力争？","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cfe75bae0f","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：能。（当代表谈通过文化大革命。革命职工胸怀祖国。放眼世界时）","index":22,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3209c49200","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：我解释一下放眼世界。过去支援亚非拉建设，特别是纺织厂都是上海派人，为什么北京不能去，支援刚果（布）建设，建议你们京棉三厂派一个男的，一个女的。    代表：可以多去。","index":23,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"15eede0981","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：不需要多去，只需要二个。一个男的，一个女的。去非洲的天气很热，去了不要想家，我到你们这里已经第五次了。","index":24,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dfd26a7c0f","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：总理来我们厂是第一次，前四次是去二厂的。","index":25,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"40be5e165b","type":"paragraph","text":"这时候总理向刚果（布）总理讲：群众批判我了，说我来得少。","index":26,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4ca721ad78","type":"paragraph","text":"（当说到二厂厂长宋汀是走资派时）","index":27,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9081daef7d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：我建议你们很好地学习毛主席语录223页第三段，我们敢于做自我批评就是胜利，不做自我批评，就是失败。","index":28,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a0e1f88678","type":"paragraph","text":"（随后到车间参观，下面是总理参观时的问话）","index":29,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f1e7224c06","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们联合怎么样？","index":30,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ebefe9bdc5","type":"paragraph","text":"代表：组织上联合了，思想上还没有联合起来。","index":31,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bfc6d558b1","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：这是符合实际情况，今天的汇报是军管写的。还是群众写的。","index":32,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"601266f048","type":"paragraph","text":"军代表：由于时间很紧，他们写好了，没有审查。","index":33,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7dc4d51114","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：要实事求是嘛！反映些具体情况就好了。","index":34,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a71e5d9393","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（当走到粗纱车间时问）一台车有多少纱锭？","index":35,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d8bc938d15","type":"paragraph","text":"（一位其它车间工人没有答上来）","index":36,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"48fa1802a5","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：这是资产阶级和修正主义管理工厂的一套，只让工人了解一点，不了解全面。要好好学习。","index":37,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cfef30115e","type":"paragraph","text":"工人答：明天就学。","index":38,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"98a59ccb88","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：今天就要学。","index":39,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7f2e12fa92","type":"paragraph","text":"参观到2时许，离厂。","index":40,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5345b893b3","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}